body.p:
Littaṃ
paramena tejasā, gilamakkhaṃ
puriso na bujjhati;

Evampi
lokāmisaṃ opatanto, vihaññatī
cittavasānuvattī;

Disvā
khurappe dhanuveganunne, khagge
gahīte tikhiṇe teladhote;

Dvāsattati
gotama bho gotama (ka.) puññakammā, vasavattino
jātijaraṃ atītā;

Tānissa
kammāyatanāni assu, purisassa
vuttisamodhānatāya;

Samaṇe
tuvaṃ brāhmaṇe addhike ca, santappayāsi
annapānena bhikkhaṃ;

Yo
sabbalokassa nivātavutti, itthīpumānaṃ
sahadārakānaṃ;

Neva
kiṇāmi napi vikkiṇāmi, na
cāpi me sannicayo ca atthi idhatthi (syā.);

Ye
kecime suggatimāsamānā suggatimāsasānā (sī. pī.), suggatāsisamānā (ka.), dhamme
ṭhitā saṃyame saṃvibhāge;

Na
te naṭā no pana kīḷaneyyā, na
bandhavā no pana te sahāyā;

Cando
ca suriyo ca ubho sudassanā, gacchanti
obhāsayamantalikkhe;

Upanīyati
jīvitamappamāyu, jarūpanītassa
na santi tāṇā;

Anānutappāni
hi ye karonti, vibhajja
kammāyatanāni loke;

Na
puttahetu na dhanassa hetu, na
āyuno cāpi vāpi (sī. pī.) janinda hetu;

Rājā
ca pabbajjamarocayittha, raṭṭhaṃ
pahāya naravīraseṭṭho;

Na
khattiyoti na ca brāhmaṇoti, na
aḍḍhakā balavā tejavāpi;

Vissāsamāpajjimahaṃ
acelaṃ acelo (sī. pī.), samaṇo
ayaṃ sammato bhāvitatto;

‘‘Sayaṃ
āyaṃ
vayaṃ āyavayaṃ (pī.) jaññā, sayaṃ jaññā katākataṃ;

‘‘Ekāyane
taṃ pathe addasaṃsu, balena
vaṇṇena cupetarūpaṃ;

‘‘Mutto
tuvaṃ porisādassa hatthā, gantvā
sakaṃ mandiraṃ kāmakāmī;

‘‘Nabhañcaṃ
dūre pathavī ca dūre, pāraṃ
samuddassa tadāhu dūre;

‘‘Anindriyabaddhamasaññakāyaṃ
nirindriyaṃ antaṃ asaññakāyaṃ (sī. pī.), anidriyaṃ santamasaññakāyaṃ (syā.), vessānaraṃ
kammakaraṃ pajānaṃ;

‘‘So
aggamā rājagahaṃ surammaṃ, aṅgassa
rañño nagaraṃ durāyutaṃ durāsadaṃ (syā.);

‘‘Āmāyadāsāpi
bhavanti heke, dhanena
kītāpi bhavanti dāsā;
